This can also be a sign of excessive CPU usage.  If you are using video compression, reduce the load by switching to a faster codec or tweaking the quality and keyframe intervals.  Also, if you know how, check to see if bus mastering (DMA) is enabled on y
our capture drive.
\par \pard \widctlpar 
